<del rend="strikethrough">v </del> nye <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r1l11">wöllet / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / Vnd het Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ Juden </ab>
