</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_184" id="92r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen von Wysentaw czu Pewlndorff gesessen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, uns hat
                            <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Strölein, jude, hie bey uns gesessen,
                        wie ir in auf den Rötpach gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geladen habt,
                        und wir euch doch des rechten von im <expan>ze helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> nye
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir von
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet; das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
                        juden icht <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
<expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir euch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinb<ex>oten</ex></expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>
                        etc. Und lat uns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen bey disem poten. </ab>
</div>
